cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks for translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves the retrieval of phrase pairs from a corpus.
